      - RT #62095: prevent XSS
      - RT #62095: persistent message on /login
      - RT #63057: typo
      - RT #64087: typos
      - RT #64126: Use precise name of licence
      - RT #64126: typos
      - RT #67820: fix relationship decleration
      - Do not recommend FastMmap
    - DevelopmentProcess
      - RT #62610: typo

5.8005 27 Oct 2010
